nodes.text: A female individual at one point became a duchess of the planet Malastare and was considered ancient by the time Qui-Gon Jinn was the Padawan of Jedi Master Dooku. According to legend, the duchess had a daughter who became a Dark Jedi, while her father waged wars that were vicious even by the standards of Malastarians. These familial connections led Jinn to interpret an ancient Jedi prophecy about a female individual who was born into and gave birth to darkness as referring to her.
The Duchess of Malastare was mentioned in the 2019 novel Master & Apprentice, written by Claudia Gray.
